N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 1020.1 - Application and definitions

State Regulations

This Part serves as a supplement to, and must be read
in conjunction with, the Rules of the Appellate Division, All Departments Part
1240 - Rules for Attorney Disciplinary Matters of this Title. In the event of a
conflict, Part 1240 of this Title shall control. This Part incorporates the
definitions set forth in section
1240.2
of this Title. Unless
otherwise specified, any reference herein to "the Court" or "the Appellate

Division" refers to the Appellate Division, Fourth Department. Notes
